<section>
<title></title>

<para>

This is a simple example to check the behavior of the 
<xml:tag>r:expr</xml:tag> tag.
Here we have <xml:expr>&lt;r:expr&gt; sum(1:10)&lt;/r:expr&gt;</xml:expr>
and we want the value 55 to displayed.
So here it is: <r:expr>sum(1:10)</r:expr>.

</para>

